00:59:34.240 --> 00:59:37.450
Your gut needs to be more acidic
than essentially all other

00:59:37.450 --> 00:59:40.000
tissues of your body in
order to function properly,

00:59:41.180 --> 00:59:44.490
bacteria thrive in alkaline conditions.

00:59:44.490 --> 00:59:46.180
I think this is important
for people to understand.

00:59:46.180 --> 00:59:47.200
People are always thinking, oh,

00:59:47.200 --> 00:59:49.420
you should be more alkaline being acidic,

