01:00:05.720 --> 01:00:08.710
to essentially combat acid reflux,

01:00:08.710 --> 01:00:11.860
which is the sending up of stuff

01:00:11.860 --> 01:00:13.793
in the gut towards the esophagus.

01:00:14.690 --> 01:00:16.380
And it can cause heartburn
and things of that sort.

01:00:16.380 --> 01:00:20.790
And the way the antacids
work is they essentially

01:00:20.790 --> 01:00:23.480
cause the sphincters above the gut

01:00:23.480 --> 01:00:25.620
to sinch shut, but they
really are only dealing

01:00:25.620 --> 01:00:27.770
