rather than mentioning all
along is to highlight a specific

01:39:44.840 --> 01:39:47.510
point, which is that whenever
we hear about the vagus

01:39:47.510 --> 01:39:50.050
in popular culture, it's like
the vagus calms you down,

01:39:50.050 --> 01:39:51.640
you want to stimulate the vagus by rubbing

01:39:51.640 --> 01:39:54.080
in front of the ear, and
it's a parasympathetic nerve,

01:39:54.080 --> 01:39:55.690
and it will calm you down,
he'll mellow you out.

01:39:55.690 --> 01:39:59.760
Actually, most of the time,
