01:40:09.832 --> 01:40:11.010
it makes you more alert and go seek more

01:40:11.010 --> 01:40:13.703
of those foods or what
led to those conditions.

01:40:14.880 --> 01:40:16.727
When you feel nauseous
it's rarely calming,

01:40:16.727 --> 01:40:20.140
when you feel like you have
a fever, it's rarely calming.

01:40:20.140 --> 01:40:21.790
So you're starting to
get the picture that even

01:40:21.790 --> 01:40:25.805
though the vagus nerve is in
the parasympathetic branch

01:40:25.805 --> 01:40:27.550
