01:40:27.550 --> 01:40:28.740
And if that doesn't mean anything to you,

01:40:28.740 --> 01:40:31.000
because you're not in
aficionado, don't worry about it.

01:40:31.000 --> 01:40:35.350
But it's not a calming system,
it's a communication system,

01:40:35.350 --> 01:40:36.530
and it's a motor system.

01:40:36.530 --> 01:40:38.830
It communicates brain to
body and body to brain,

01:40:38.830 --> 01:40:41.943
and it changes the function
of different organs, now,

01:40:43.270 --> 01:40:47.240
one thing that's important
to highlight is that stress

01:40:47.240 --> 01:40:51.600
itself will alter the
chemistry of your gut

01:40:51.600 --> 01:40:54.910
because of the ways that
it down the vagus nerve

01:40:55.775 --> 01:40:58.170
and quiets the neurons that
communicate from gut to brain.

01:40:58.170 --> 01:40:59.290
I want to say that again,

01:40:59.290 --> 01:41:01.130
stress will disrupt your gut

01:41:01.130 --> 01:41:04.878
and make you feel not
good, poor digestion,

01:41:04.878 --> 01:41:07.890
and just lousy, because
of the way that it shuts

01:41:07.890 --> 01:41:10.730
down the vagus nerve and
the neurons of your gut.

01:41:10.730 --> 01:41:13.930
So what stress does is it
blocks the communication

01:41:13.930 --> 01:41:16.770
