01:41:59.690 --> 01:42:02.000
of your gut, the conditions of your heart

01:42:02.000 --> 01:42:03.930
and the conditions of your breathing,

01:42:03.930 --> 01:42:07.480
which includes your diaphragm
and lungs and takes that kind

01:42:08.850 --> 01:42:11.490
of as a collection of
information and sends it

01:42:11.490 --> 01:42:14.873
